THREE STRIKES POLICY

Serious or repeated rule violations are handled progressively:

  Strike 1: Written warning from staff, logged.
  Strike 2: Temporary ban (duration set by staff).
  Strike 3: Permanent removal from the game.

Not every incident uses this ladder. Severe harassment, cheating, or
attempts to harm the server may skip directly to a permanent ban.

SEE ALSO: rules, harassment, reporting
